      <div class="project_name">
          <h6>Theo Hand</h6> <br>
          <h8>hyper-personal prosethetic </h8> <br>
          <ul> Press
          <li><span class="jacobs"> <a href="http://jacobsinstitute.berkeley.edu/student-project/theohand/">Jacob's Project Spotlight</a> </span></li>
          <li><span class="ways"><a href="https://medium.com/@CalAdmissions/5-ways-uc-berkeley-students-lead-in-world-changing-research-40380f9faa00">5 ways UCB students lead</a> </span></li>
          </p>

