      <div class="design_overview">
        <h7> Our Solution/ Design Overview </h7>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col">
            <li>Soft robotic fingers</li>
            <li>  Turning knob </li>
            <li>  Locking ratchet </li>
            <li>  Velcro straps</li>
            <li>  Stationary thumb </li>
            <li>  Attaches to bicep and forearm </li>
            <li>  Release switch </li>
            <li>  Grasp feedback with fsr led feedback </li>
            <li>  Bionic aesthetic</li>
          </div>

